{"tid":1477572,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］香港老師 817 遊行（內有洋蔥）","createTime":"2019-08-16T07:19:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T15:07:08.000Z","uid":193510,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa3dd25d0f44865282868b77387f6d5e928feb2","tid":1477572,"uid":193510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:19:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/APRFT6UEtBE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAPRFT6UEtBE&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=b0f5b3ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/APRFT6UEtBE</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/1nu1a2q9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2F1nu1a2q9&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=c1c81057\" target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/1nu1a2q9</a><br />\n<br />\n👩🏻&zwj;🏫👨🏻&zwj;🏫《我地係香港老師》作出緊急呼籲📣<br />\n<br />\n教師大遊行（教協主辦）<br />\n日期：8月17日<br />\n時間：上午11時集會、11時半起步<br />\n路線：中環遮打花園至禮賓府<br />\n<br />\n721<br />\n元朗黑社會無差別攻擊事件，<br />\n警局拉閘拒絕救援。<br />\n至今仍然冇人被起訴<br />\n<br />\n811<br />\n警察射傷女救護員右眼球<br />\n可能導致永久失明，<br />\n警察在地鐵站施放催淚彈，<br />\n近距離向示威者開槍<br />\n假扮示威者，<br />\n還拘捕示威者後插贓嫁禍。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭日久，血流得越多，<br />\n難道你到現在還要退縮？<br />\n當權者的冷漠與殘暴，就是要禁聲。<br />\n我們連集會示威的權利也被限制，<br />\n可能有機會在路過時吸入催淚煙，<br />\n有機會行街被警察追打和拘捕。<br />\n既是如此，你還沉默下去嗎？<br />\n<br />\n老師，<br />\n我們在過去兩個經歷過失望和恐懼，<br />\n面對沉重的無力感，<br />\n<br />\n你願不願意站出來，<br />\n與我們同行？<br />\n<br />\n良知，你還在嗎？<br />\n<br />\n守護下一代 為良知發聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n📣教育界 資訊傳播Channel:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFClJ47fhJzsgC3JBw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFClJ47fhJzsgC3JBw&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=61b86980\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFClJ47fhJzsgC3JBw</a><br />\n<br />\n🌻我地係香港老師Instagram: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/wearehongkongteachers?igshid=1af17uuu43z8x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fwearehongkongteachers%3Figshid%3D1af17uuu43z8x&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=8d21cad2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/wearehongkongteachers?igshid=1af17uuu43z8x</a><br />\n<br />\n❤️我地係香港老師FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WeareHongKongTeachers/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWeareHongKongTeachers%2F&d=bx%2Fd%2Fc%2BwyKmxZhRK7gjal3jCBy0DQDxxpn8JrxrWeYE%3D&h=24a5bf25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WeareHongKongTeachers/</a>"},{"pid":"76a7a498b32bfec5592d7a9bde146834b346d7dd","tid":1477572,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:20:06.000Z","msg":"普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7a102eb8d89d0d82589f43a510aba0fc0c0ad4de","tid":1477572,"uid":292881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:20:33.000Z","msg":"推呀 817 817 817"},{"pid":"749f268e7fd490de30f9b275ab756c08c2297520","tid":1477572,"uid":292881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:20:52.000Z","msg":"有良知就一齊推<br />\n<br />\n［突發］(我知我P牌）香港老師 817 遊行（內有洋蔥）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1477340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1477340</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"676a2faa4595c06fb147007e1d0dba79b25719bd","tid":1477572,"uid":193510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"守護學子  堅守良知"},{"pid":"a2e5a75fc66309b5611c9ae4d85aec6cec43fcf4","tid":1477572,"uid":218501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"676a2faa4595c06fb147007e1d0dba79b25719bd","tid":1477572,"uid":193510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"守護學子  堅守良知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T07:26:04.000Z","msg":"Respect<img src=\"/assets/